snippet.title: WATCH: Sentencing phase gets underway in trial of Amber Guyger
snippet.description:
Amber Guyger faces 5 to 99 years in prison. The jury will determine her punishment. The jury found the former Dallas police officer guilty of murder Tuesday in the shooting death of her neighbor over a year ago. 
Here's a look back at the trial: https://www.kgw.com/article/news/crime/amber-guyger-murder-trial-daily-breakdown-livestream/283-7c0187eb-efc0-4170-a847-3d69aff27eb4
